   <S PAR='1' RSNT='1' SNO='1'>PREFACE</S>
   <S PAR='2' RSNT='1' SNO='2'>Volume 51 of The Collected Works contains messages given by Watchman Nee in a training for co-workers and elders at Kuling Mountain in China in 1948.</S>
   <S PAR='3' RSNT='1' SNO='3'>These messages were originally published in Chinese.</S>
   <S PAR='4' RSNT='1' SNO='4'>The English edition is based on the fourth edition of the book which was printed in December 1982 by the Juridical Party of Taiwan Gospel Book Room.</S>
   <S PAR='5' RSNT='1' SNO='5'>The contents of Volume 51 have been published previously by Living Stream Ministry under the title Church Affairs.</S>
   </TEXT>
